name: Digital Nomad
description:
Life as a Digital Nomad is one of my daily activities, since the Pandemic occurred in 2020 many Salaryman ( and us designers) has been forced to work remotely from home.
As of now, lots of people still working remotely away from their offices, they have worked remotely from our home, apartments, even from other countries.

…and now I’m kinda getting used to it.

Aren't you?
